con:config.con:query: SELECT ACNT.EMAIL Member_Email, ACNT.id member_id, PROV.EMAIL Coach_Email,SMRY.ACCOUNT_PROGRAM_ID FROM SUMMARY_ACCOUNT_TODATE SMRY, PROVIDER PROV, ACCOUNT ACNT WHERE PROV.ID=SMRY.ASSIGNED_PROVIDER_ID AND SMRY.ACCOUNT_ID=ACNT.ID AND SMRY.ONBOARDING_STATUS='MEMBER ONBOARDED' AND ACCOUNT_ID IN (SELECT ACCOUNT_ID FROM ACCOUNT_PROGRAM WHERE ACCOUNT_PROGRAM.START_DT_TIME>SYSDATE + INTERVAL '-52' DAY AND ID IN (SELECT ACCOUNT_PROGRAM_ID FROM ACCOUNT_PROGRAM_SESSION_DETAIL WHERE SESSION_STATUS!='Completed')) AND ACCOUNT_ID IN (SELECT ACCOUNT_ID FROM ACCOUNT_MEASUREMENT WHERE ACCOUNT_MEASUREMENT.STARTING_WEIGHT >0 AND ACCOUNT_MEASUREMENT.ACCOUNT_ID = ACNT.id) AND PROV.Email='coach12342@yopmail.com' AND (select Count(Subject) from Message where Message.TO_USER_ID = ACNT.id)>0 ORDER BY SMRY.SESSION_DATE_UTC DESC
